&lt;figure&gt;
&lt;img alt="" src="https://game.donga.com/media/__sized__/images/2025/2/21/d2de8f5cfbbb4e1d-thumbnail-1920x1080-70.jpg"/&gt;
&lt;figcaption&gt;
